603
00:29:43,172 --> 00:29:44,347
OKAY, YOU HAVE
TO HELP ME.

604
00:29:44,391 --> 00:29:45,827
SHE'S ONE OF
THE BETTER ONES.

605
00:29:45,871 --> 00:29:47,307
BETTER ONE WHAT?

606
00:29:47,350 --> 00:29:49,091
WHAT'S THE PROBLEM, GEORGE?

607
00:29:49,135 --> 00:29:51,528
