SHE WON'T FOLLOW ME.

608
00:29:51,572 --> 00:29:53,226
NINA FORGETS THINGS.

609
00:29:53,269 --> 00:29:54,575
YEAH, I PICKED UP
ON THAT.

610
00:29:56,490 --> 00:29:59,667
