620
00:30:25,388 --> 00:30:26,912
OH, COME ON. PLEASE?

621
00:30:26,955 --> 00:30:29,001
SORRY, HONEY, CAN'T DO IT.

622
00:30:29,044 --> 00:30:30,350
COME ON. I DON'T...

