630
00:30:56,071 --> 00:30:57,333
PEANUT.

631
00:31:01,120 --> 00:31:02,991
<i>I WOULD NEVER BECOME OLD.</i>

632
00:31:03,035 --> 00:31:05,951
<i>DEAD AND YOUNG
